## 4. Session Workflow

```
1. Read AGENTS.md (first session only, or for reference)
2. Read STATUS.md -> find task
3. Read task file -> follow context header
4. Implement (max 6 files read before coding)
5. Test: {{PKG_MANAGER}} test && {{PKG_MANAGER}} build
6. Update STATUS.md -> mark task done
7. Add work log entry
8. Update LEARNINGS.md if you discovered something new
```
